extended_title: Fairphone 5 Android smartphone. Announced Aug 2023. Features 6.46″  display, QCM6490 chipset, 4200 mAh battery, 256 GB storage, 8 GB RAM, MIL-STD-810H compliant, Corning Gorilla Glass 5.
Fairphone 4 Android smartphone. Announced Sep 2021. Features 6.3″  display, Snapdragon 750G 5G chipset, 3905 mAh battery, 256 GB storage, 8 GB RAM, MIL-STD-810G compliant, Corning Gorilla Glass 5.
Fairphone 3+ Android smartphone. Announced Aug 2020. Features 5.65″  display, Snapdragon 632 chipset, 3040 mAh battery, 64 GB storage, 4 GB RAM, Corning Gorilla Glass 5.
Fairphone 3 Android smartphone. Announced Aug 2019. Features 5.65″  display, Snapdragon 632 chipset, 3040 mAh battery, 64 GB storage, 4 GB RAM, Corning Gorilla Glass 5.
